    "biography": "<p>Fantastic creatures with the legs and body of a horse, and the upper body and head of a human. Live in small family or tribal groups, in wild meadows and isolated forests.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Weapons: </strong>Bows, clubs, lances.</li>\n<li><strong>Lair: </strong>Hidden in dense woods, along twisting, guarded paths.</li>\n<li><strong>Females and young: </strong>Normally remain in the lair. Flee if attacked. Young have 2HD and make 2 hoof attacks (1d2) and 1 weapon attack (1d4 or by weapon).</li>\n</ul>"
